snippet.title: Release Date Trailer - Heaven Studio
snippet.description:
EVERYTHING IN THIS VIDEO IS SUBJECT TO CHANGE

It's almost here! Heaven Studio is launching on January 15th, 2024!
Heaven Studio is a (WIP) Fully playable open source recreation of every Rhythm Heaven minigame, with a built in level editor!
After 2 years in development, our first release includes around 50 games, with more to come in future releases.

Level created by @thatzeogal 
Song (Heaven Studio Title Theme) created by @SushiiZProductions ‪https://twitter.com/realsushiiz
Thumbnail created by @saladplainzone 
Thumbnail art created by @minenice4890 & ev

GitHub  - https://github.com/RHeavenStudio/HeavenStudio
Discord - https://discord.gg/2kdZ8kFyEN
itch.io - https://rheavenstudio.itch.io/heaven-studio

Rhythm Heaven is the intellectual property of Nintendo. This program is NOT endorsed nor sponsored in any way by Nintendo. All used properties of Nintendo (such as names, audio, graphics, etc.) in this software are not intended to maliciously infringe trademark rights. All other trademarks and assets are property of their respective owners. This is a community project and this is available for others to use according to the GPL-3.0 license, without charge.
